summary: Code Genie - Embark on a journey into the future of web development with Code Genie. Our pioneering platform leverages artificial intelligence to effortlessly translate visual designs into functional code. By automating the design-to-code process, Code Genie boosts efficiency, shrinks development timelines, and democratizes web development for all. Anchored by the Code Genie token, our unique tokenomics model ensures economic sustainability and incentivizes active participation within the Code Genie community.
